Here's the PlantUML sequence diagram for the vishipayyallore_blazorwasm-apim-api-sql-redis system, focusing on the control flow during a book retrieval operation:

```plantuml
@startuml vishipayyallore_blazorwasm-apim-api-sql-redis

actor User
participant "Blazor WASM" as Blazor
participant "Azure API Management" as APIM
participant "BooksController" as API
participant "BooksBll" as BLL
participant "BookCacheRepository" as Cache
participant "BookRepository" as SQL
database "Redis" as Redis
database "SQL Server" as SQLDB

User -> Blazor: Requests book list
Blazor -> APIM: GET /api/books
APIM -> API: Forward request
API -> BLL: GetBooks()
alt Cache hit
    BLL -> Cache: GetBooks()
    Cache -> Redis: GET books
    Redis --> Cache: Return cached data
    Cache --> BLL: Return books
else Cache miss
    BLL -> SQL: GetBooks()
    SQL -> SQLDB: SELECT * FROM Books
    SQLDB --> SQL: Return books
    SQL --> BLL: Return books
    BLL -> Cache: CacheBooks(books)
    Cache -> Redis: SET books
end
BLL --> API: Return books
API --> APIM: Return HTTP 200 with books
APIM --> Blazor: Return response
Blazor --> User: Display books

@enduml
```